        <div class="arch-layer-desc">A hardened desktop minting station allows the Governor to initialise Digital Money Bundles. Generates CVIB units with Ed25519 cryptographic signatures, delivered via secure SFTP/NAS channels.</div>
      </td>
      <td class="arch-arrow-cell">&#8594;</td>
      <td class="arch-box">
        <span class="arch-layer-num">Layer 02</span>
        <span class="arch-layer-title">Registry Layer</span>
        <span class="arch-layer-sub">Commercial Banks &mdash; API Validation Desk</span>
        <div class="arch-layer-desc">An API-based validation desk ingests CVIB files, verifies signature integrity, and checks against the National Registry. Ensures every CBDC unit undergoes a full lifecycle audit from minting to redemption.</div>
      </td>
      <td class="arch-arrow-cell">&#8594;</td>
      <td class="arch-box">
        <span class="arch-layer-num">Layer 03</span>
        <span class="arch-layer-title">Corridor Layer</span>
        <span class="arch-layer-sub">Cross-Border Settlement &mdash; DLT Engine</span>
        <div class="arch-layer-desc">A specialised DLT engine manages FX rate resolution and liquidity pool backing across all 54 AU corridors, enforcing economic sovereignty with 1:1 reserve backing per corridor pair.</div>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>

